596
00:45:45,525 --> 00:45:47,058
Nothing.

597
00:45:47,060 --> 00:45:50,428
I-I thought you said that you
wanted to be a vegetarian!

598
00:45:50,430 --> 00:45:51,863
No. I said...

599
00:45:51,865 --> 00:45:53,997
that confined animal
feeding operations

600
00:45:53,999 --> 00:45:56,333
are the largest cause
of greenhouse gases,

601
00:45:56,335 --> 00:45:59,069
and that we should only buy
from small local farms.

602
00:45:59,071 --> 00:46:01,071
I swear, you have
selective hearing.

603
00:46:01,073 --> 00:46:03,740
<i>Do not talk to me
that way, Lauduree!</i>

604
00:46:03,742 --> 00:46:07,076
I'm really tired of this
"miss know-it-all attitude."

605
00:46:07,078 --> 00:46:08,778
Now, if you're gonna be
living in this house...

606
