real cute figure.

614
00:47:12,939 --> 00:47:14,404
Crystal's friend.

615
00:47:14,406 --> 00:47:16,706
That's the one.

616
00:47:16,708 --> 00:47:18,675
Nah, I ain't seen
here in a while.

617
00:47:18,677 --> 00:47:21,411
Crystal was in here
the other night, though.

618
00:47:21,413 --> 00:47:24,414
She was showing me pictures
of her chihuahua.

619
00:47:24,416 --> 00:47:25,714
Lucky you.

620
00:47:25,716 --> 00:47:27,883
Them things are freaky.

621
00:47:53,108 --> 00:47:54,441
<i>Hello?</i>

622
00:47:54,443 --> 00:47:56,843
Hi, is Neel home?

623
00:47:56,845 --> 00:47:59,545
<i>This is Neel.</i>

624
00:47:59,547 --> 00:48:02,448
<i>Is this Lauduree?</i>

625
00:48:02,450 --> 00:48:04,417
<i>- Yes.
- Hi.</i>

626
00:48:08,188 --> 00:48:12,056
Do you want to find
some pigtoes tomorrow?

627
00:48:22,134 --> 00:48:24,001
Let's get started, baby!

628
00:48:26,806 --> 00:48:29,206
- Hey, Crystal!
- Whoo!

629
00:48:29,208 --> 00:48:31,041
Hey!

630
00:48:31,043 --> 00:48:32,843
I need to talk to you.

631
00:48:32,845 --> 00:48:34,844
Oh, hey, Greta, I'm workin'.
You wanna come in for a drink?

632
00:48:34,846 --> 00:48:37,013
No, not really.

633
00:48:37,015 --> 00:48:39,582
Are you still working
nights at the V.A.?

634
00:48:39,584 --> 00:48:40,716
Like a rat in a can.

635
00:48:42,053 --> 00:48:45,587
So you got a number
where she's at.

636
00:48:45,589 --> 00:48:47,956
- Who?
- Cut the crap, Crystal...

637
00:48:47,958 --> 00:48:49,524
'Cause you know what
I'm picturing right now?

638
00:48:49,526 --> 00:48:51,927
I'm picturing her real high on crank.
Good lord!

639
00:48:51,929 --> 00:48:53,895
In a horse barn turned
into a meth lab

640
00:48:53,897 --> 00:48:56,131
with the lowlife that
you turned her on to.

641
00:48:56,133 --> 00:48:58,766
I'm gonna go back inside, baby.

642
00:48:58,768 --> 00:49:00,868
Cruiser!

643
00:49:03,171 --> 00:49:04,805
Look, Greta,

644
00:49:04,807 --> 00:49:06,774
I'm in the same boat you are.

645
00:49:06,776 --> 00:49:09,242
I haven't heard from her in two weeks,
and I'm worried to death.

646
00:49:09,244 --> 00:49:12,645
I can tell when you're
lying, Crystal,

647
00:49:12,647 --> 00:49:15,715
'cause you are the one that
taught Tanya how to do it.

648
00:49:15,717 --> 00:49:17,951
Oh, little ol' me, huh?

649
00:49:17,953 --> 00:49:20,219
I just wanna know
if she's alive.

650
00:49:23,823 --> 00:49:25,991
Okay, I'm gonna level with you.

651
00:49:27,927 --> 00:49:29,561
Ree thinks she's dead.

652
00:49:29,563 --> 00:49:33,998
She won't eat. She won't sleep.
She won't bathe.

653
00:49:34,000 --> 00:49:36,200
