683
00:51:47,021 --> 00:51:49,088
Don't touch it!

684
00:51:51,157 --> 00:51:52,658
You need a permit.

685
00:51:52,660 --> 00:51:53,759
Oh.

686
00:51:55,862 --> 00:51:58,130
